reviewText: Someone storyboarded this in a semester of Bible class. Spanish Jesus is heroic with a sense of humor.
Hilarious!  Especially if you know your Bible stories.  I recommend it for believers with a sense of humor and non-believers alike.  Jesus surely kicks butt in this short film.
One of the funniest films ever. Even if you are a believer, it's hilarious.
Oh my God I liked to have died laughing. Both times. My husband lost his breath he laughed so hard. We're both Christians but we have to acknowledge the humor in such things.
